Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.35,0:18:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,流水
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.65,0:18:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,只是打個招呼而已嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.99,0:18:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不過也讓他看到「流水」了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.14,0:18:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.45,0:18:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.66,0:19:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不會有人突破陷阱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.60,0:19:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,馬克斯  沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.94,0:19:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,而且就算被破了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.65,0:19:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,還有各位可靠的同伴在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.63,0:19:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,真擔心呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.32,0:19:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,要是寶珠被搶走會挨罵的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.95,0:19:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,這次的襲擊者也中了陷阱 遍體鱗傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是「陷阱師」馬克斯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.59,0:19:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.04,0:19:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是設陷阱一直在等待而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.96,0:19:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.46,0:19:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,蜜伊會連我們的份一起 把寶珠拿回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.18,0:19:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,炎帝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,噴火
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,爆炎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.62,0:19:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,這是MP藥水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.27,0:19:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.15,0:19:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,去回收寶珠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.64,0:19:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我去追
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.42,0:20:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你們拿著現有的寶珠先回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.34,0:20:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,焰火飛馳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.24,0:20:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,瞬影…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.01,0:20:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,炎帝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.86,0:20:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,炎帝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.76,0:20:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,炎帝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.01,0:20:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,炎槍  炎槍  炎槍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.35,0:20:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,炎帝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,被逃掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.87,0:20:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,大家對不起啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.21,0:20:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,其實我不適合當首領的說…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.32,0:20:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,下次再遇上絕對要打敗你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.44,0:20:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是那些女人的據點啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.04,0:20:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不會錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.04,0:20:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡有我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.25,0:20:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不對  是我們的寶珠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.66,0:20:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.46,0:20:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,話說我們還是第一次 8個人一起戰鬥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.86,0:20:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,經妳一說好像是那樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.76,0:20:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,梅普露  麻煩妳出老招了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.97,0:20:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:20:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,搶回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.12,0:21:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的驕傲和寶珠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.14,0:21:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,動手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.31,0:21:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.64,0:21:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼啊
