Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.81,0:21:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,真卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.63,0:21:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦  永別了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.70,0:21:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,起碼也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.67,0:21:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,看我這刀
