Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.77,0:01:58.42,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}飛進另一個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:04.70,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}幼年夢想的憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.72,0:02:07.80,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}是畫在天空上的女主角
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.83,0:02:10.56,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}踏出小小的一步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.57,0:02:13.96,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}便翻開了書本的內頁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.00,0:02:17.40,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}特別的奇蹟邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.42,0:02:20.17,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}全都是珍貴回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.19,0:02:23.22,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}異想天開的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.25,0:02:25.65,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}招來了奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.68,0:02:29.66,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}終極的不均衡
