Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.03,0:22:48.67,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}所謂的偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.69,0:22:52.13,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}必定是命運開始轉動
